  步骤2: 1.000x  [Convert the conditional branch inside the inner loop (i loop) into a branchless computation: replace the if-block 'if (a[i] > b[i]) { a[i] += b[i] * c[i]; }' with the expression 'a[i] += b[i] * c[i] * (float)(a[i] > b[i]);'. This uses the comparison result as a boolean mask (0.0 or 1.0) to multiply the product, making the addition unconditional. The transformation eliminates branch misprediction overhead and enables the compiler to generate masked vector instructions or select operations, improving throughput and potentially enabling SLP vectorization that was previously blocked by the branch. The result is numerically identical because adding zero (when condition is false) does not change the value of a[i].]

